@Social_HostAddress = http://localhost:5120
@Token = {{$dotenv JWT_TOKEN}}

### Feed page 1 (cursor pagination)
GET {{Social_HostAddress}}/api/v1/posts/feed?limit=20

### Feed next page (cursor = CreatedAt of last post, ISO-8601)
GET {{Social_HostAddress}}/api/v1/posts/feed?limit=20&cursor=2026-05-22T10:00:00.0000000+00:00

### User wall (public posts by author)
GET {{Social_HostAddress}}/api/v1/posts/user/{{userId}}?limit=20

### My wall (JWT — includes private posts)
GET {{Social_HostAddress}}/api/v1/posts/me/wall?limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}

### User media gallery (only posts with media)
GET {{Social_HostAddress}}/api/v1/posts/user/{{userId}}?limit=20&onlyMedia=true

### Backfill share codes for legacy posts (Development / AllowShareCodeBackfillApi)
POST {{Social_HostAddress}}/api/v1/posts/maintenance/backfill-share-codes
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}

### Post by share code (deep link)
GET {{Social_HostAddress}}/api/v1/posts/share/AB12CD34

### Create post
POST {{Social_HostAddress}}/api/v1/posts
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "postType": "Standard",
  "content": "Hello SYNC community!",
  "mediaUrls": [],
  "isPublic": true,
  "authorSnapshot": {
    "fullName": "Test User",
    "avatarUrl": null
  }
}

### Like post (atomic Interaction + $inc LikeCount)
POST {{Social_HostAddress}}/api/v1/posts/{{postId}}/like
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}

### Create comment
POST {{Social_HostAddress}}/api/v1/posts/{{postId}}/comments
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Hay quá!",
  "authorSnapshot": { "fullName": "Test User", "avatarUrl": null }
}

### List comments (offset pagination)
GET {{Social_HostAddress}}/api/v1/posts/{{postId}}/comments?pageNumber=1&pageSize=20

### Create community challenge (JWT) — auto-posts to feed
POST {{Social_HostAddress}}/api/v1/challenges
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Chạy 50km tháng 5",
  "description": "Cùng nhau chạy đủ 50km trong tháng này!",
  "startDate": "2026-05-01T00:00:00Z",
  "endDate": "2026-05-31T23:59:59Z",
  "goalType": "TotalDistance",
  "targetValue": 50,
  "authorSnapshot": { "fullName": "Admin SYNC", "avatarUrl": null }
}

### Active challenges
GET {{Social_HostAddress}}/api/v1/challenges/active

### Share post (legacy interaction endpoint)
POST {{Social_HostAddress}}/api/v1/posts/{{postId}}/interactions
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "interactionType": "Share"
}
